PokeAPI (Big Database) -Dedicated Server - Dedicated Database - Front End Client
Type + Pokemon (id & name) Get Routes -> Dedicated Server -> PokeAPI Data -> Filter Data-> Saved in Dedicated Database    
Collection Route ->Dedicated Server-> Dedicated Database 
Post Route ->Dedicated Server-> Dedicated Database 
Delete Route ->Dedicated Server-> Dedicated Database 


